{"id": 559, "genre": 1001, "title": "有哪些用力过猛的电影译名？", "description": "因为这我差点错过一部好电影。", "record_count": 14936, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194446ARLzvu5WJcTdQrpg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-05T01:10:36Z", "options": [{"id": 25344, "content": "大破天幕杀鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272169}, {"id": 14852, "content": "欲盖弄潮，看起来好色情?了其实很温暖吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162821}, {"id": 15365, "content": "必须是放牛班的春天！！！！听名字以为是中国乡土片！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197525}, {"id": 18693, "content": "人体蜈蚣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249188}, {"id": 15110, "content": "我必须得说那个丧尸片《活死人黎明了》………评论里好多人问为什么没有找到黎明 还有人说他居然真的看见黎明了 还有人问为什么不叫活死人张学友？？？？什么鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231505}, {"id": 16390, "content": "这个杀手不太冷，总以为是搞笑片", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245047}, {"id": 15623, "content": "《美丽心灵》《美丽心灵的永恒阳光》", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234870}, {"id": 14857, "content": "火星人玩转地球，要不是大师蒂姆伯顿的作品，看这么二的名字就感觉是烂片", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209723}, {"id": 15369, "content": "《失落的大陆》以为是个沧桑的纪录片～谁知道是来逗乐的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234150}, {"id": 15625, "content": "《极速风流》两个男人的封面，心想这又是怎么弯男片。没想到很直", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236342}, {"id": 14858, "content": "一直想不明白图灵传记电影为啥叫做《模仿游戏》", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227197}, {"id": 14859, "content": "后天", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215666}, {"id": 15371, "content": "farewell my concubine—霸王别姬（再见我的小妾）?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222836}, {"id": 19211, "content": "魔力麦克。。。当初总觉得好怂！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263408}, {"id": 14861, "content": "心灵捕手那个，Will Hunting是人名……乍一看和天使爱美丽差不多，但人家那个勉强说通，这个就是纯粹脑补好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55088}, {"id": 15373, "content": "比利怀德的one.two.three，翻译成了玉女风流。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150745}, {"id": 14862, "content": "\n《前目的地》，这部电影的译名让我觉得像是一部异国风情游历纪录片，结果看完才知道，这特么是部烧脑神作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 192980}, {"id": 15630, "content": "小時代", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236385}, {"id": 14863, "content": "超能六战队", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185657}, {"id": 14865, "content": "难道不是 无极 咩～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215591}, {"id": 14866, "content": "婚纱 乍一看以为是爱情片", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227409}, {"id": 14870, "content": "夏洛特烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227444}, {"id": 15126, "content": "绿灯侠，闪电侠，蜘蛛侠，是不是要有红灯侠，月亮侠，蚂蚱侠", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231635}, {"id": 20502, "content": "电锯惊魂，TMD哪来的电锯？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266166}, {"id": 14871, "content": "看了很多评论…深感赞同。电影的名字起得不好真的有可能会错过很多观众唉。记得一部定格动画《卡洛琳》，中文翻译成《鬼妈妈》，反正我是很好奇得看了。如果我只看到卡洛琳这个电影名我很可能不会去看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214075}, {"id": 15127, "content": "v字仇杀队！经典电影这个真的，虽然和电影主题是很相关，没看之前以为是个什么特工队培训的复仇故事好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201975}, {"id": 14873, "content": "俄罗斯的有一部电影叫穿越火线…", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214089}, {"id": 15129, "content": "周董，不能说的秘密", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231669}, {"id": 14875, "content": "黑客军团", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227564}, {"id": 15643, "content": "need for speed 极品飞车…", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158535}, {"id": 15645, "content": "闻香识女人 每次向同学推荐都会被投以邪恶的目光  还问我番号", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236551}, {"id": 15136, "content": "《两杆大烟枪》我还以为是讲鸦片战争的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231731}, {"id": 14881, "content": "《搏击俱乐部》听名字真觉得是很无聊的电影，没想到其实那么精彩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227766}, {"id": 14882, "content": "我绝对是被“放牛班的春天”给雷到了，以为是很土的乡村教一个班级放牛的孩子的故事，结果看了以后发现简直是高逼格的，太好看了，牛爆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227800}, {"id": 14883, "content": "第一次看见煎饼侠 觉得是类似于某羊羊一样的国产神片 最后了解才发现是一部不错的片子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225883}, {"id": 14885, "content": "速度与激情这名字就够low了 台湾竟然翻译成夺命光头...", "image": null, "praise_count": 312, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223245}, {"id": 14886, "content": "撒娇女人最好命，次兔兔好命了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227969}, {"id": 15911, "content": "跪求周立波很大[笑cry]吴奇隆胸记[笑cry]井柏然并卵[笑cry]贾乃亮了[笑cry]权志龙虾壳[笑cry]", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238657}, {"id": 14888, "content": "煎饼侠", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227989}, {"id": 14889, "content": "三傻大闹宝莱坞", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219892}, {"id": 15913, "content": "跪求周立波很大[笑cry]吴奇隆胸记[笑cry]井柏然并卵[笑cry]贾乃亮了[笑cry]权志龙虾壳[笑cry]", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238657}, {"id": 21802, "content": "《九层妖塔》……我活该被骗！电影宣传什么的都是骗人的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281718}, {"id": 14892, "content": "《要听神明的话》OMG不听话就得死……就得死……得死……死…让我对神有新的认识了 ", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211922KCcUjETJhR0Q9N8d.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216096}, {"id": 14893, "content": "异形大战铁血战士 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188907}, {"id": 15149, "content": "007大破量子危机，007大破天幕危机，007大破幽灵危机……愣是把一个酷酷的英国特工拉到了黑猫警长的画风。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5509}, {"id": 14896, "content": "三傻大闹宝莱坞", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223756}, {"id": 15152, "content": "挨饿游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179498}, {"id": 14899, "content": "你们知道米高左顿 是Michael Jordan嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225178}, {"id": 16181, "content": "歌功颂德 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242220}, {"id": 14902, "content": "《赤焰战场》卧槽我一看以为是飞机坦克大炮狂轰滥炸，一个个军人为了国家抛头颅洒热血“赤焰”这么猛的词肯定是一个精英小队的队名，结果尼玛虽然很好看但是我想找那个翻译片面的人练练。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228315}]}